text: It is a good value for money Korean restaurant inside the hawker. The saba fish is very flavourful, and the rice is cooked on point. Too little kimchi is served and the veggie below the fish is inexistent.
Salmon omelette curry rice = $6.50 + 30 cents for takeaway
The curry like soup. Taste is real bad... The staff doesn't seems interested in cooking. Gave wrong order.
